% Psychological Status box
ULOrigin PageWidth LM RM add sub 242 box
ULOrigin 23 sub moveto
RMx CurrentY lineto
stroke

Header setfont
ULOrigin 18 sub dup 3 -1 roll moveto
(PSYCHOLOGICAL STATUS) cshow

Body setfont

% Psychological Status
% --------------------

% Headers for checkboxes
(Evaluation Rating) BodyLeftEdge      	ULOriginY 55 sub   moveto   show
(Not At All)        ULOriginX 168 add 	ULOriginY 55 sub   moveto   uscoreShow
(Mild)              ULOriginX 258 add 	ULOriginY 55 sub   moveto   uscoreShow
(Moderate)          ULOriginX 323 add 	ULOriginY 55 sub   moveto   uscoreShow
(Serious)           ULOriginX 403 add 	ULOriginY 55 sub   moveto   uscoreShow
(Severe)            ULOriginX 482 add 	ULOriginY 55 sub   moveto   uscoreShow

% define the starting position and interval to move down each line
/LinePosition ULOriginY 78 sub def
/Interval -15 def
% Column positions
[ ULOriginX 189 add
  ULOriginX 266 add
  ULOriginX 343 add
  ULOriginX 418 add
  ULOriginX 495 add ]
% Position Reporting strings
[(  NotAtAll) (  Mild) (  Moderate) (  Serious) (  Severe)]

[(Anger)  (Relationship Disorder) (Depressive State)    (Anxious State) 
 (Phobic) (Thought Disorder)      (Behavioral Problems) (Substance Abuse / Dep)
          (Homicidal Potential)   (Suicidal Potential)  (Memory Problems)] {
  dup = % for reporting position
  ULOriginX 20 add LinePosition moveto show 
  0 1 4 {
    2 copy get exch    % Get the position report string and exch
    3 index exch get   % Get the X coord from the array
    LinePosition       % Y coord
    moveto reportPos
    currentpoint CBSize boxOnLine   % and draw a checkbox
  } for
  /LinePosition LinePosition Interval add def
} forall
mark 3 1 roll cleartomark % clean up - remove the two arrays

% Bottom box
% ----------
ULOrigin 257 sub PageWidth LM RM add sub 396 box
ULOrigin 469 sub moveto
RMx CurrentY lineto
stroke

